   Science & Engineering Teams


                                  Team Name

                                   Purpose

                                  Team Lead
   ISIM
   [Integrated Science
   Instrument Module]
   Group charged with developing an integrated power-thermal-mechanical
   structure to house NGST science instruments

                                   VACANT

   Operability Team studying observatory and science instrument issues
   that affect the subsequent operations of the mission

                             J. Isaacs, (STScI)

   Optical Testing Devise methods for testing of optics of NGST including
   facilities consideration

                            R. Keski-Kuha (GSFC)

   Science

   Science team interacts with astronomical community, project engineers
   and managers to assure that the science goals of NGST are realized

                              J. Mather (GSFC)
   Systems Engineering

   Provide system integration and oversight for the entire observatory

                               J. Burt, (GSFC)
   Technology Foster technology studies in areas of interest to NGST

                               R. Burg, (GSFC)

   Smaller groups

   Smaller, focused study teams or teams whose work has been completed.




